		<div id="siteNotice"><script type='text/javascript'>if (wgNotice != '') document.writeln(wgNotice);</script></div>		<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading">Belief</h1>
		<div id="bodyContent">
			<h3 id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</h3>
			<div id="contentSub"></div>
									<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->
			<div class="dablink">For other uses, see <a href="/wiki/Believe_(disambiguation)" title="Believe (disambiguation)" class="mw-redirect">Believe (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
<p><b>Belief</b> is the psychological state in which an individual holds a <a href="/wiki/Proposition" title="Proposition">proposition</a> or <a href="/wiki/Premise" title="Premise">premise</a> to be true.<sup id="cite_ref-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-0" title=""><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup></p>
